<div id="philosophy"class="container">
  <h1 class="text-center">Mobile first design</h1>
  <p>Since late <%= link_to "2016", "http://gs.statcounter.com/press/mobile-and-tablet-internet-usage-exceeds-desktop-for-first-time-worldwide", target: "_blank", class: "voyagr" %>, worldwide mobile and tablet internet usage has exceeded desktop usage. This means that websites designed without mobile and tablet users in mind will be excluding over half of their potential audience. As such, my goal is to provide for this preponderant group first, ensuring that there is no loss of functionality or design as a result of varied device usage.</p>
